description: Subregional Youth Parliamentarians for Tokelau and Niue Project

subproject.description:
1. Establishment of a National Youth Officer post for continued advocacy and awareness on youth issues raised at the highest government levels.
2. A National Youth Parliament session in Tokelau and Niue held to provide an opportunity for young people to learn about government and governance
3. At least one sharing of best practice through South-South Cooperation between Tokelau, Niue and/or other neighbouring Pacific Island Countries (PIC)
subproject.title: Subregional Youth Parliamentar
